### Register a new test user (Successful Case)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testrunner@example.com",
  "password": "secure_password123",
  "confirmPassword": "secure_password123"
}

### Register a new test user (Intended Failure - Password Mismatch)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mismatchrunner@example.com",
  "password": "correct_password123",
  "confirmPassword": "incorrect_password321"
}

### Attempt to create a run WITHOUT a token (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning 5K",
  "startTime": "2026-07-16T12:00:00Z"
}

### Create a run WITH a valid token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_COPIED_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Morning 5K",
  "startTime": "2026-07-16T12:00:00Z",
  "totalDistance": 5000,
  "totalDuration": 1500,
  "route": [
    {
      "latitude": 43.4516,
      "longitude": -80.4925,
      "timestamp": "2026-07-16T12:00:00Z"
    }
  ]
}